General.Name: Card Factory PLC
General.Description: Card Factory plc operates as a specialist retailer of cards, gifts, and celebration essentials in the United Kingdom and internationally. The company operates through five segments: Cardfactory Stores, Cardfactory Online, Getting Personal, Partnerships, and Printcraft. It provides greeting cards, celebration essentials, and gifts through cardfactory stores retail and cardfactory online retails, and network of third-party retail partners; and personalised cards and gifts through online retailer, as well as manufactures and sells greeting cards and personalised gifts through printcraft stores and online businesses. The company offers its products through various retail locations, as well as through its websites, such as cardfactory.co.uk and gettingpersonal.co.uk. It also offers printers; and operates as a intermediate holding company. Card Factory plc was founded in 1992 and is headquartered in Wakefield, the United Kingdom.
General.Address: Century House, Wakefield, United Kingdom, WF2 0XG
